(129, '_transient_dash_552322dd4badcfc6c46e921c5ef2a928', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/11/wordpress-4-4-beta-3/''>WordPress 4.4 Beta 3</a> <span class="rss-date">4 noviembre, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4 Beta 3 is now available for download and testing. This is software still in development, so we don’t recommend that you run it on a production site. To get the beta, try the WordPress Beta Tester plugin (you’ll want “bleeding edge nightlies”). Or you can download the beta here (zip). For more of what’s new in version 4.4, check out [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/how-not-to-communicate-grievances-with-wordpress''>WPTavern: How Not to Communicate Grievances with WordPress</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/jetpack-3-8-adds-google-badges-and-fixes-contact-form-response-emails''>WPTavern: Jetpack 3.8 Adds Google+ Badges and Fixes Contact Form Response Emails</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/11/most-miles-of-road-texas/''>Matt: Most Miles of Road: Texas</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpclef/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Clef Two-Factor Authentication</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=wpclef&amp;_wpnonce=4008292a55&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Clef Two-Factor Authentication''>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
